<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 14:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列和真主党的威慑平衡取决于哈马斯在开罗的协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</link><description>真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉再次表示，尽管以色列努力将黎巴嫩问题单独对待，但只有在加沙达成停火后，才会在北部边境达成协议。球在以色列这边，但以色列对真主党的要求不仅仅是停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 12:12:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-hezbollah-deterrence-formula-will-be-decided-by-an-israel-hamas-deal-in-cairo/0000018d-a740-dd3b-a5df-bfcbeee80000</guid></item><item><title>SUV 盗窃浪潮引发人们对约旦河西岸再次发生 10 月 7 日式袭击的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</link><description>过去几周，以色列发生了铃木吉姆尼盗窃案。许多人再次出现在约旦河西岸，导致一些人担心这些盗窃行为是袭击计划的迹象</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:49:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/a-spike-in-thefts-of-mini-suvs-from-israel-to-the-west-bank-raises-concerns/0000018d-a736-d9a5-afdd-b77ffb6d0000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射火箭弹，导致一名以色列人死亡、八人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</link><description>炮火攻击的目标是以色列北部城市萨法德的一个军事基地；以色列国防军表示正在回应并打击黎巴嫩的火源</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 11:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/one-israeli-killed-eight-wounded-in-rocket-barrage-fired-from-lebanon-on-northern-israel/0000018d-a6f6-dc34-afed-a6f7ba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属前往国际法庭敦促起诉哈马斯领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</link><description>以色列不是国际刑事法院成员，也不承认其管辖权，但检察官卡里姆·汗本周重申，该法院对 10 月 7 日事件拥有管辖权。人质家属代表团希望法院逮捕哈马斯领导人认股权证</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/families-of-israeli-hostages-visit-icc-to-urge-the-arrest-of-hamas-leaders/0000018d-a716-d9a5-afdd-b75f72590000</guid></item><item><title>“严重关切”：犹太领导人致信以色列外长，谴责部长们与瑞典极右翼政党的会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</link><description>在给以色列外交部长的一封信中，欧洲犹太人大会和瑞典犹太社区理事会的领导人警告不要与瑞典民主党结盟，信中称瑞典民主党“自称是我们的盟友”，同时主张“犹太人不能是瑞典人” .&amp;#39;该党根源于新纳粹和反犹太主义意识形态</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/gravely-concerned-jewish-leaders-decry-ministers-meeting-with-far-right-swedish-party/0000018d-a35c-d42f-adcd-ebfcbac60000</guid></item><item><title>瑞安航空表示，由于战时低成本航站楼关闭，该公司取消了飞往以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</link><description>瑞安航空在 10 月 7 日取消飞往以色列的航班后仅两周前就续签了部分航线。这家总部位于都柏林的航空公司在周二发布的一份声明中表示，“期待在低成本航站楼 1 号航站楼重新开放后恢复运营”。打开&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 10:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/ryanair-says-cancelled-flights-to-israel-due-to-wartime-low-cost-terminal-closure/0000018d-a6a9-dc34-afed-a6bb945f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列担心更多西方国家会效仿制裁暴力的西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-additional-western-countries-will-follow-suit-in-sanctioning-violent-settlers/0000018d-a6a3-d9a5-afdd-b7eff18b0000</link><description>法国效仿美国和英国，选择不等待欧盟的决定。一位以色列高级政治人物表示，如果政府不对暴力定居者执行法律，这可能会为制裁以色列士兵和领导人打开大门</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 09:59:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-fears-additional-western-countries-will-follow-suit-in-sanctioning-violent-settlers/0000018d-a6a3-d9a5-afdd-b7eff18b0000</guid></item><item><title>议会小组将权衡针对个人表达的极右翼反煽动法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-to-weigh-tougher-anti-incitement-laws-targeting-individual-expressions/0000018d-a403-d8e9-a3bf-f7234e9a0000</link><description>民间社会团体和公设辩护人办公室反对这些法案，认为这些法案没有必要且反民主。民权倡导者警告说，这可能相当于思想警务</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 04:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-to-weigh-tougher-anti-incitement-laws-targeting-individual-expressions/0000018d-a403-d8e9-a3bf-f7234e9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团参加开罗人质谈判的余地有限——内塔尼亚胡并不急于达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-sent-its-delegation-to-cairo-but-a-hostage-deal-is-not-their-top-priority/0000018d-a424-d400-a7cd-ffa7bd490000</link><description>总理继续坚称，军事压力最终将导致以色列达成一项条件更好的协议，无论人质家人如何抗议。看来新的人质协议并不是以色列代表团的首要任务</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 04:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-sent-its-delegation-to-cairo-but-a-hostage-deal-is-not-their-top-priority/0000018d-a424-d400-a7cd-ffa7bd490000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军在一名以色列人死亡后开始对黎巴嫩进行“大规模”打击；巴勒斯坦总统敦促哈马斯交换人质</t