ar-what-you-need-to-know-day-130/0000018d-a388-d8e9-a3bf-f3a8285e0000</link><description>摩萨德负责人、辛瓦尔在开罗与卡塔尔、埃及调解人进行停火/人质释放谈判的副手 ■ 南非就以色列即将在拉法实施的军事行动与国际法院接洽 ■ 法国表示将对袭击西方巴勒斯坦平民的 28 名定居者实施制裁银行 ■ 真主党的纳斯鲁拉表示，他的组织“致力于与以色列作战，直到以色列消失为止” ■ 以下是战争 130 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 18:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-130/0000018d-a388-d8e9-a3bf-f3a8285e0000</guid></item><item><title>法国与美国和英国一起制裁 28 名“极端主义”以色列约旦河西岸定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/joining-the-u-s-and-u-k-france-sanctions-28-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018d-a311-d42f-adcd-ebf1ff310000</link><description>法国外交部还呼吁在更广泛的欧洲范围内实施类似的制裁。极右翼议员 Tzvi Succot：“不民主的程序，完全是根据极左组织的一时兴起而进行的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 17:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/joining-the-u-s-and-u-k-france-sanctions-28-extremist-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018d-a311-d42f-adcd-ebf1ff310000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉称真主党“致力于与以色列作战，直到它从地图上消失”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-hezbollah-is-committed-to-fighting-israel-until-it-is-off-the-map/0000018d-a2f9-d42f-adcd-ebf9b64f0000</link><description>真主党领导人哈桑·纳斯鲁拉在周二的讲话中表示，在加沙达成停火之前，他不会同意与以色列达成协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 16:08:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/nasrallah-says-hezbollah-is-committed-to-fighting-israel-until-it-is-off-the-map/0000018d-a2f9-d42f-adcd-ebf9b64f0000</guid></item><item><title>说唱之战：意大利音乐节因针对以色列的种族灭绝指控而震动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/rap-battle-italian-music-festival-rocked-by-genocide-accusations-against-israel/0000018d-a1fb-d416-a3ed-edfb50ac0000</link><description>圣雷莫音乐节通常都是为了挑选一位当地代表参加欧洲歌唱大赛。当犹太社区无意中放大了亲巴勒斯坦说唱歌手的信息时，今年的版本变得丑陋</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 15:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/rap-battle-italian-music-festival-rocked-by-genocide-accusations-against-israel/0000018d-a1fb-d416-a3ed-edfb50ac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在纽约特别选举中争夺众议院席位的激烈竞争中占据中心地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-takes-center-stage-in-head-to-head-battle-for-house-seat-in-nys-special-election/0000018d-a1fa-d92c-a9ed-ebfb60bd0000</link><description>在周二被驱逐的议员乔治·桑托斯 (George Santos) 的众议院席位争夺战中，共和党候选人、美国以色列国防军退伍军人马兹·皮利普 (Mazi Pilip) 与亲以色列的前民主党人展开对决。众议员汤姆·索齐</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 14:51:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-takes-center-stage-in-head-to-head-battle-for-house-seat-in-nys-special-election/0000018d-a1fa-d92c-a9ed-ebfb60bd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列改革运动就极端正统派学生的征兵日期向高等法院请愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-high-court-over-draft-date-of-ultra-orthodox-students/0000018d-a287-d42f-adcd-ebe72bcc0000</link><description>以色列军队宣布，在以色列与哈马斯战争期间，将提前招收陆军预科学生的征兵日期，但并未提前招收任何极端正统派犹太学院学生</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 14:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-reform-movement-petitions-high-court-over-draft-date-of-ultra-orthodox-students/0000018d-a287-d42f-adcd-ebe72bcc0000</guid></item><item><title>追寻马可波罗去世 700 年后的圣地足迹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-02-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tracing-marco-polos-footsteps-in-the-holy-land-700-years-after-his-death/0000018d-a241-d416-a3ed-eefb33300000</link><description>学者和历史学家仍在研究历史上最著名的旅行家的生活和旅行。在他向东的旅程中，威尼斯贸易在阿卡和耶路撒冷停止，十字军、蒙古人和马穆鲁克人在那里争夺控制权</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 13:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/2024-02-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tracing-marco-polos-footsteps-in-the-holy-land-700-years-after-his-death/0000018d-a241-d416-a3ed-eefb33300000</guid></item><item><title>以色列母子被黎巴嫩反坦克导弹击中重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mother-and-son-severely-wounded-by-anti-tank-missile-fire-from-lebanon/0000018d-a252-d42f-adcd-ebf239410000</link><description>这名妇女和她十几岁的儿子在基里亚特什莫纳市的车里，一枚导弹落在他们旁边，两人都受了重伤；副市长说：“汽车被炸飞了，他们下了车，然后第二枚导弹击中了他们。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 12:23:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-mother-and-son-severely-wounded-by-anti-tank-missile-fire-from-lebanon/0000018d-a252-d42f-adcd-ebf239410000</guid></item></channel></rss>